messages.message: Hi @Jasper, we haven't pushed anything to aihub EU for a while given that it was in active use.  Maybe Microsoft changed some things in their end.
Thanks, @shaunak. Are we planning to support aihub.eu (http://aihub.eu) in the long run and if yes will we push the latest version to it again and some point?
Yes, we are planning to support it.  I'll check in with the SE team to see when there is good time to update it.
